  <description type="morphology">Seta 3–5 mm, straight to some-what arcuate.  Capsule when mature narrowly ovoid to nearly cylindric, 3–5 mm, dull brown to rusty-brown, upper face not strongly differentiated from lower face, slightly oblique to seta or nearly erect.  Spores 12–13 µm.</description>
  <description type="morphology">Capsules mature late summer–fall.</description>
